title: D&D Next 5th Edition
description:
I finally found The Rise of Tiamat, so here's a new upload of the old Torrent.


Thought it would be nice to compile all of the currently released (minus Rise of Tiamat) major D&D 5th edition books.  No mini-adventures are included, nor are any of the freely available downloads (except Basic Rules, because why the hell not).

Player's Handbook
Monster Manual
Hoard of the Dragon Queen
Rise of Tiamat

Plus Starter Set
Basic Rules
Lost Mine of Phandelver
Character Sheets
